Cell["Here\[CloseCurlyQuote]s the greatest function that was ever created", \
"Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.983514706361827*^9, 
  3.9835147254406557`*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"8a8c941a-fb09-42ce-abf7-\
